    instruction: "The emotional arc guides you through four stages. Recognize: name what is happening inside you. Allow: let it be here without trying to fix or push it away. Investigate: get curious about where it lives in your body and what it needs. Nurture: offer yourself the kindness you would give a dear friend. Each stage builds on the previous one.",
